data.description: Short sale. MOVE IN READY!! This beautiful home features the owner's suite on the main level, beautiful crown molding, and a double-sided fireplace situated between the family and keeping rooms. You will love the true hardwood flooring in the high traffic areas. The keeping room is large with space to seat 6 at the table, an additional lounging area and a built-in desk so the cook will not miss out on the conversations. There is an island separating the cooking area, plenty of cabinets, a large pantry and an additional storage closet. The large laundry room including a laundry sink has additional storage space or even room for a folding table, ironing or an additional freezer. The owner's suite with elegant tray ceilings offers a a sitting area, double vanities in the bath with a beauty station, a soaking tub with separate shower, closed lavatory and a huge walk-in closet. Upstairs there are 3 additional bedrooms and a bonus. One bedroom has it's own bath and there is an additional shared bath with separate vanities. The finished bonus room is perfect for an office, playroom or crafting area. The finished space in the basement includes an additional bedroom and bath as well as another finished room which could be used as a game room or another living area. The heating and air conditioning is already available throughout the basement and is just waiting for you to come make the additional space fit your needs. Outdoors there is an expansive deck off the keeping room which includes a large beautiful cedar arbor for relaxing in the shade. Down below at the basement level is a large patio. Enjoying the beautiful landscaping and flower beds. If you enjoy gardening there is even sunlit space to grow your own veggies. Don't miss your chance at this spacious home located at the end of a cul-de-sac in an established community without the additional expense of an HOA. Schedule to view today.
